sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor AT as Attendee
    participant EEP as Edit Event Page
    participant DJ as Django Web App
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant OS as Object Storage

    %% Open form
    AT->>EEP: Open create / edit event page
    EEP-->>AT: Display create / edit event form

    %% Submit details
    AT->>DJ: Submit event details, ticket info, optional media
    DJ->>DJ: Validate inputs and business rules

    %% Persist core data
    DJ->>PG: Save core event details (title, desc, date, etc.)
    DJ->>PG: Save ticket details (price, availability, categories)
    DJ->>PG: Set slug and publish state
    PG-->>DJ: Return success confirmation

    %% Optional media
    opt Upload media
        DJ->>OS: Store images / banners / videos
        OS-->>DJ: Return media URLs
        DJ->>PG: Save media URLs
        PG-->>DJ: Return success confirmation
    end

    %% Success and visibility
    DJ-->>AT: Redirect / Display event page
